==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[trundle]] [[bed]]'''
#a bed designed to be rolled or stored away, typically under another bed, usually for temporary use when guests arrive
#a bed where one takes a [[trundle]]. The bed is not normally used to take a [[trundle]] whilst guests are using it.
#a type of bed often taken on long canoeing expeditions which functions both as a bed and a [[trundle]] [[repository]].

